title: Martin Molloy (1995) The Brown Album - Disc 2 (Browner Still)
description:
The Brown Album is the first compilation double-album of material taken from the Australian radio program Martin/Molloy, with comedians Tony Martin and Mick Molloy. The Brown Album won the Best Comedy Release at the 1996 ARIA Music Awards, as did the two following Martin/Molloy albums in subsequent years.
